Well, I think that your side's strategy probably should have been to remove or weaken the other side's artillery before mounting your assault. <P>Paladins are not a 'weak' class per se; it's more likely that your organization was just lacking, and a disorganized team (or one that pays no respect to ranged attacks) is not going to be successful very often.<P>--------------------<P>Trost - 9 Scout<BR>Ronaldus - 7 Wizard<BR>Begbie - 9 Armsman<BR>Oreilly - 12 Friar<BR>Tristan Server<P>Bresh - 7 Druid<BR>Lancelot Server<P>Enduring - 7 Beserker<BR>Dubya - 5 Hunter<BR>Igrane Server
